messages.message:
I’ve been using the app quite a lot on site at Cass the last few days. Their CEO described it as ‘transformational to his business’. Cass have poured a tonne of effort and money into building a reconciliation tool which compares values invoiced against contracted charges. We built it on AI Hub in under 5 mins live with them in the room. There hasn’t been a single person we’ve shown it to that wasn’t stunned with the power it will provide them.

The responses in chat are now super fast too, almost too fast, it responds quicker than I can think of what to say next in my demo :clap:
Thanks for sharing the feedback, @Lee! We’re thrilled to see the customer impact. It is exactly what the whole team has been working and hoping for!
